Industrial Union of Donbass, a
Ukrainian corporation, is considering a merger of its steelmaker
PAT  Alchevskiy Metalurgiyniy Kombinat (ALMK)  and coke and chemicals
producer PAT Alchevskiy Koksochemical,  Interfax-Ukraine  newswire
reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Taras Shevchenko.  To contact the reporter on this story:
